name: Dulint
title: Guardian of the Cube
description: Dulint is an elderly dwarf miner and trader, great-grandson of Thrain Ironbeard. He carries an ancient artifact unknowingly and guards dangerous secrets, believing silence will protect those he cares for.
descriptiones: Dulint es un enano anciano minero y comerciante, bisnieto de Thrain Ironbeard. Lleva un artefacto antiguo sin saberlo y guarda secretos peligrosos, creyendo que el silencio protegera a quienes aprecia.
